snippet.title: Commando+Ninja Emaki=Mighty Guy Arcade Game LONGPLAY 1cc Gameplay (マイティガイ Nichibutsu 1986) MAME
snippet.description:
Mighty Guy arcade game Longplay Full Playthrough 1cc gameplay one credit all (1 loop). Capcom Commando+Ninja Emaki=Mighty Guy (マイティガイ Nichibutsu 1986). Mighty Guy Gameplay , very rare arcade game. Juego retro arcade PCB jeu, spiel, fliperama. GOOD Sound Emulation with MAME 0.20 arcade emulator. No cheats, game completed with 1 credit / juego completado con 1 crédito y USB arcade joystick Welcom WE-6100 arcade controller (my review https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOQF6eI1fJA). Mighty Guy fast run (one loop / una vuelta).

ニチブツ アーケード クラシックス / Nihon Busan. Other arcade classics from Nichibutsu: Rolling Crash / Moon base, Crazy Climber, Moon Cresta ムーンクレスタ, Moon Quasar, Seicross, Tube Panic チューブパニック (fujitek / nichibutsu), Galivan Cosmo Police コスモポリス ギャリバン, Mag Max, Terra Cresta テラクレスタ, Dangar Ufo Robo ロボ ダンガー, Ninja Emaki / Youma Ninpou Chou, Soldier Girl Amazon 聖戦士アマテラス, Kodure Ookami, Sky Fox / Exerizer (jaleco / nichibutsu), Terra Force.
